&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="6-schedule-pods-on-the-master">6. Schedule Pods on the Master
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>By default the control-plane is tainted to avoid user workloads. To allow pods on your micro-server master:&lt;/p>
