&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Now you can deploy pods (e.g. your Dashboard or small cronjobs) on that same box.&lt;/p>
